title: Disney's DTV Monster Hits - Halloween special
description:
Back when Disney use to play awesome Halloween specials every year, they aired this awesome show called DTV Monster Hits. It\&#039;s basically a bunch of spooky themed Disney cartoon clips put to spooky themed music.
